P_HTM[5666]="*Chaṭṭhaṃ.* **";
P_HTM[5667]="*6. Dasamaggasuttaṃ**Bad Character (1st)*";
P_HTM[5668]="*“Pāpañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi, pāpena pāpatarañca;**“Mendicants, I will teach you who’s bad and who’s worse,*";
P_HTM[5669]="*kalyāṇañca, kalyāṇena kalyāṇatarañca. Taṃ suṇātha … pe ….**who’s good and who’s better.*";
P_HTM[5670]="*Katamo ca, bhikkhave, pāpo?**And who’s bad?*";
P_HTM[5671]="*Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco pāṇātipātī hoti … pe … micchādiṭṭhiko hoti.**It’s someone who kills living creatures, steals, and commits sexual misconduct. They use speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, or nonsensical. And they’re covetous, malicious, with wrong view.*";
P_HTM[5672]="*Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, pāpo.**This is called bad.*";
P_HTM[5673]="*Katamo ca, bhikkhave, pāpena pāpataro?**And who’s worse?*";
P_HTM[5674]="*Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco attanā ca pāṇātipātī hoti, parañca pāṇātipāte samādapeti … pe … attanā ca micchādiṭṭhiko hoti, parañca micchādiṭṭhiyā samādapeti.**It’s someone who kills living creatures, steals, and commits sexual misconduct. They use speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, or nonsensical. They’re covetous, malicious, with wrong view. And they encourage others to do these things.*";
P_HTM[5675]="*Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, pāpena pāpataro.**This is called worse.*";
P_HTM[5676]="*Katamo ca, bhikkhave, kalyāṇo?**And who’s good?*";
P_HTM[5677]="*Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti … pe … sammādiṭṭhiko hoti.**It’s someone who doesn’t kill living creatures, steal, or commit sexual misconduct. They don’t use speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, or nonsensical. And they’re contented, kind-hearted, with right view.*";
P_HTM[5678]="*Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, kalyāṇo.**This is called good.*";
P_HTM[5679]="*“Katamo ca, bhikkhave, kalyāṇena kalyāṇataro?**And who’s better?*";
P_HTM[5680]="*Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco attanā ca pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti, parañca pāṇātipātā veramaṇiyā samādapeti … pe … attanā ca sammādiṭṭhiko hoti, parañca sammādiṭṭhiyā samādapeti.**It’s someone who doesn’t kill living creatures, steal, or commit sexual misconduct. They don’t use speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, or nonsensical. They’re contented, kind-hearted, with right view. And they encourage others to do these things.*";
